Name: Mosaique Neko Waifus 5
About the game: Let's take a quick hike, shall we? How could you say no? This is how your adventure with Kumi starts. Neko girls always give you this weird feeling of hiding a little secret. But having unexpected encounters with Nekos always has a happy end, so why not just relax and let it all happen? • Enjoy the unique puzzles • Use special abilities that help you solve puzzles • Also level them up, mix and match, and create your builds • Navigate the different dialogue choices. Be nice! • Collect items after each solved puzzle and boost your skills. 100 Items to collect in total • View all the scenes unlocked in the gallery • 20 Puzzles • 100 Achievements
